        </paragraph>
      </subsection>
      <subsection commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="H759C1566251F4EB3B3D7494D3E9DD4EA">
        <enum>(b)</enum>
        <header>Effective
			 date</header>
        <text>The amendments made by this section shall apply to taxable
			 years beginning after December 31, 2013.</text>
      </subsection>
    </section>
