			 Code of 1986</cato:entity-ref> is amended by striking <quote>beginning before January 1,
			 2010</quote> and all that follows and inserting “beginning—</text>
        <quoted-block display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id62C796D95E6440B4A0C5B4BCA15D9684" style="OLC">
          <subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="idD8609323B3CC41FD8DF0E5B927FB1968">
